                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-87-victim958 t18310217-87-viclabel534"></join>. About half-past two o'clock in the afternoon, on the 14th of January, I saw Radley take this pair of shoes from a board at his shop - he and Baker ran off; I took them both, and took the shoes from Radley - they had been in company before.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Radley's Defence. This <rs id="t18310217-87-deflabel535" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-87-defend954 t18310217-87-deflabel535"></join>
